snippet.title: Above & Beyond Duality
snippet.description:
*** NEW SERIES COMING SEPT 2022! 3D to 5D: How To Make The Shift ***

Welcome to Above & Beyond Duality! We are a full time team of channellers, graphic artists and animators and we build custom spiritual animations and messages for YouTube. Here's a typical process for one of our videos:

1) Transcribe/receive message (into text)
2) Quality check grammar
3) Record VoiceOver/send to VoiceOver team
4) Select music & layer to VoiceOver
5) Import audio & build animation
6) Finishing touches

Each video typically takes about a day to build (often more!) and we're going full steam, full time to get you daily content! We use some of the industries top animation software including: Blender, UE5, Adobe After Effects, Final Cut Pro, Adobe Premiere and MORE! If you have any questions please reach out anytime: info@abovebeyondduality.com

Namaste. 

David + Team
